<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>169</hymn_number>
<author>Ngama</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka pienna thim lal kulhpi,
 Vak mu dingin Aw Isu;
 Na cha gitloh suoka tangsa,
 Na theihna khut hattak chun;
 Nawpna kimna gam nuom chuh,
 Lungsietin ei tunsak in.

[V2]
 Chun, kipak tangka Lalpa,
 Chun nunnuom tang ie Isu;
 Lei gimumna haw chu taihsan in,
 Angel tuollenna gitloh beihna;
 A chun kumsawt in chawl ka.

[V3]
 2. Zie gam chu tung thei dingin,
 Theihna bang ahim ka neih?
 Nangmah theihna ngei ahi Pa,
 Vak muhna ding lampi chu;
 Keile tuhin ka chang tai,
 Ei siem muolsuoh ngei dingin.

[V4]
 3. Ka sunga umhaw lakah,
 A neupen chuh Nang na hi;
 Ahih ziekin, ka Lal liengvai,
 Vaihawmpa hatpen hi din;
 Tuhin chuh hun chiel tangka,
 Bangcheng nang thu thu hi hen.

[V5]
 4. Thiengtho ingka, Nangmah thu'n,
 Khawvel thil thil ta loin;
 Nang kawm zawtna lampi diktak,
 Na Bible Thu hawihtak chu;
 Tuhin chu Aw ka Lalpa,
 Ka thu bulpen chu hi hen.
 5. Kipah thu gen zing ding chu,
 Ka thagau nang hi na hi;
 Gitloh tincheng mauna lakah,
 Chieh zelin, Kalvari ah;
 Kumsawt hinna na chan hi,
 Chawl lo in gen zing inla.</lyrics>
<title>Kumsawt In Chawl Ka</title>
</song>